Last post for tonight. Cya you all tomorrow.)


:KitKat:

KitKat::
She looked at Land Mine. "I don't know what in all your feeling, but 
I can guess." She sighed and thought about how unneeded and unwanted 
she was feeling too.
"I can only tell you one thing. Don't worry about the small stuff.  
For things can always be worse. Look at me, I lost an arm. But I'm 
still here and I got my arm back.  So don't worry about the small 
stuff." She looked at the blade that she had given back to Land Mine 
and thought about cutting her own arm. She shook her head. 
"look, I'm going to go hunting here in a little while. Your welcome 
to join me if you want." She got up and walked to  the door of the 
lab.
"Smile, it's not so bad."
